"&cantor; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections about the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> "
"and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</"
"ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&cantor; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा <guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> "
"मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-"
"settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /ulink> तथा च &kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "प्रश्नोत्तरम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Menu Item <guimenuitem>Typeset using LaTeX</guimenuitem> is not available"
msgstr ""
"LaTeX</guimenuitem> इत्यस्य उपयोगेन मेनू-वस्तु <guimenuitem>Typeset उपलब्धं नास्ति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not every backend supports every option. Current version supports &latex; "
"output for Maxima, Qalculate! and Sage backends."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकं पृष्ठभागः प्रत्येकं विकल्पं समर्थयति न । वर्तमानसंस्करणं &latex; अधिकतमस्य कृते आउटपुट्, "
"Qalculate! तथा Sage backends इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have installed Sage/Maxima or other supported CAS, but the appropriate "
"backend does not appear."
msgstr ""
"मया Sage/Maxima अथवा अन्यः समर्थितः CAS संस्थापितः, परन्तु समुचितः पृष्ठभागः न दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One possible explanation is that &cantor; did not correctly detect the "
"location. Go to the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &cantor;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog "
"and change the <guilabel>Path</guilabel> to the appropriate application on "
"the backend's page."
msgstr ""
"एकं सम्भाव्यं व्याख्यानं अस्ति यत् &cantor; स्थानं सम्यक् न ज्ञातवान्। "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &cantor;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> संवादं गत्वा <guilabel>Path</guilabel> इत्येतत् पृष्ठभागस्य "
"समुचिते अनुप्रयोगे परिवर्तयन्तु पृष्ठ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid "What a peculiar name - what does it have to do with mathematics?"
msgstr "किं विचित्रं नाम - गणितेन सह तस्य किं सम्बन्धः ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:965
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&cantor; is named after the German mathematician <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Georg_Cantor\">Georg Cantor</ulink>, the creator of set "
"theory."
msgstr ""
"&cantor; समुच्चयसिद्धान्तस्य निर्माता जर्मनगणितज्ञस्य <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Georg_Cantor\">जॉर्ज कैण्टर्</ulink> इत्यस्य नामधेयेन निर्मितम् "
"अस्ति ।"

